{"tid":2354693,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"如果你想救連登 打擊波台狗 就一齊入黎向連仔發表意見","createTime":"2021-01-05T15:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T16:32:07.000Z","uid":11294,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"01f69685ac3e4594f3bcd1a24603690835e3611c","tid":2354693,"uid":11294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:53:17.000Z","msg":"光復連登 CC革命 政策倡議區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2354675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2354675</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n傳送門<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc868edd58a8c3d3d37dfe7dfbb30158b2ca1258","tid":2354693,"uid":248695,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:55:12.000Z","msg":"cctoy又再一次用強權打壓意見不合嘅同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b42934fc340a03662d48edbf77092f498b7c3c","tid":2354693,"uid":11294,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong>有鑑於近日波台狗嚴重影響我地時事台手足救港<br />\n<br />\n特設呢個政策倡議區，<br />\n針對波台狗向連仔提出政策建議。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">我先拋磚引玉：<br />\n<br />\n1. 嚴禁於體育台內發表任何無關體育之貼文。<br />\n<br />\n2. 每台特設台長，由各台會員投票選出，任期為一年，可無限連任。職責為監督與防止波台狗在該台作亂，擁有將該台會員禁言一個月及刪post之權限。<br />\n<br />\n3. 唯體育台台長為委任制，由時事台資深會員輪流擔任。除普通台主權限外，擁有永久封禁違規會員之權限，任期為1個月，不設連任。<br />\n</span></strong></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4ee863bed371437ec74740849790fb5e8543375a","tid":2354693,"uid":132128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:57:49.000Z","msg":"你係連登兇我冇用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce29c7c92633c31d9f88b8d2990ab620008fac1","tid":2354693,"uid":92908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bc868edd58a8c3d3d37dfe7dfbb30158b2ca1258","tid":2354693,"uid":248695,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:55:12.000Z","msg":"cctoy又再一次用強權打壓意見不合嘅同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:58:57.000Z","msg":"有賭過波就係同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfa45256660f009b9a4c50d1cb8215a7142686a","tid":2354693,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T16:02:05.000Z","msg":"其實時事台咁鐘意一言堂咪開個論壇或者tg group圍爐囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23480355688922e0f11483c56520f3a0d5b32e5e","tid":2354693,"uid":11294,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcfa45256660f009b9a4c50d1cb8215a7142686a","tid":2354693,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T16:02:05.000Z","msg":"其實時事台咁鐘意一言堂咪開個論壇或者tg group圍爐囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"你知唔知連登邊度最多會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7235842c203a9557c028858968ba7af07d35450b","tid":2354693,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T16:06:46.000Z","msg":"，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309d70086ae8c1c917b3aa9b648ba293b8706a06","tid":2354693,"uid":11294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T16:13:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">光復連登 時事革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"040c85801eb282e85beb1a66f668d45344a79abe","tid":2354693,"uid":11294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T16:15:3